summary: So how much time has passed between 2x01 and 2x03?
title: So how much time has passed between 2x01 and 2x03?
body:
*SPOILERS*

Because episode 1 picks up right where we left off which means Konstantin was left with a bullet in his chest, and he reappears looking completely fine and healed, even though I’m pretty sure it’s been like 2 or 3 days since he got shot.

Anyone has a clear timeline?
